name: *A whole new reality will emerge*

“The burden of ignorance becomes omnipresent. More and more of the sensory experience becomes inexpressible.” Communication is love, any star can tell you that; Covering your light is motivated by shame and fear. Why do we spy on each other? This infinite regress of suspecting others is a schizophrenic logic, all your conspiracies consider only your bubble. We are faced with dilemmas and not with choices in this tension between chaos and information, we are unstable. What would you do to save yourself? We are unstable but we keep evolving. Stay optimistic. Everything will change radically and you will be the conservative.
